text: Sofian El Moudane (born 16 March 1994) is a professional French-Moroccan footballer who currently plays for Botola club Ittihad Tanger as a midfielder. ==Club career== ===FK Senica=== El Moudane made his professional Fortuna Liga debut for Senica against AS Trenčín on 16 February 2019.TRENČÍN VS.
